data.description: Must see! Updated Mid-Century Modern home located on a Cul de sac for privacy. No HOA and NEVER FLOODED per Seller. The expansive front courtyard is ideal for outdoor entertaining. We have receipts for the items taken care of for you... the Underground plumbing 2023, Foundation 2023, HVAC and Water Heater in 2023 (see feature sheet as there are too many upgrades to list here), amenities include raised ceilings, the recent roof 2016.  A Cooks' Kitchen offers Granite Countertops, SS Cooktop/Vent hood, SS Oven, SS Sink,& elongated Breakfast Bar!  The Cathedral ceilings in the Living area touts floor-to-ceiling glass doors. and vinyl CoreLuxe flooring.  The expansive primary overlooks the beauty of nature and greenery and has a overhead screened pergola. The walk in closet is amazingly huge. Be sure to check out the utility area which you won't see in every home. Roof 2016, extra wide driveway, Bellaire High School is a zoned option as well as Herod Elementary.
